content:
From: JS Lemay <js.lemay@mq.edu.au>

From: Ivan Di Liberti <diliberti.math@gmail.com>
Sent: Tuesday, October 24, 2023 4:37 AM
To: Categories mailing list <categories@mq.edu.au>
Subject: ItaCa Fest 25 October

Dear all,
I am writing to remind you that on October 25th, we have ItaCa Fest. In line with the new format, we will have 3 talks, listed below.

15:00 - 15:40 G. Lobbia, "A skew approach to enrichment for Gray-categories" 15:40 - 16:20 N. Gambino, "Monoidal bicategories, differential linear logic, and analytic functors”
16:20 - 17:00 S. R. Koudenburg, "Formal Day convolution and low-dimensional monoidal fibrations”
You can find the abstracts here: https://progetto-itaca.github.io/pages/fest23.html#oct25<https://progetto-itaca.github.io/pages/fest23.html#oct25>

The link is the usual.

https://cs-ox-ac-uk.zoom.us/j/97878376376?pwd=QithMyt5NzdOeE1EWGJRcjBxamxnUT09<https://cs-ox-ac-uk.zoom.us/j/97878376376?pwd=QithMyt5NzdOeE1EWGJRcjBxamxnUT09>

Best,
the ItaCa people.

——————————————
Ivan Di Liberti
Postdoc
Göteborgs universitet
